This file contains:
Mastermind.java that contains the code of the Mastermind game,
wich know as Bulls and Cows 
game that its matter to guess a random code at limited number of tries.
Implemention: the games begins with get inputs from the user
 belong to option of the game ,and calculate the number of bulls
 and cows and consequntly update the user results based on his
 guesses and the number of tries he can play.
link for more onformation:en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mastermind_(board_game).
I avoid repeation code as possible and I use the do-while style to avoid it! 
There is one class and One main method attached thats implement the game.
Enjoy testing it :) ! 